        "text": "verify_cell_kzg_proof_batch (SG-021) MUST validate ALL of the following before proceeding to cryptographic verification: (1) all four input lists have equal length, (2) each commitment has exactly BYTES_PER_COMMITMENT bytes, (3) each cell_index < CELLS_PER_EXT_BLOB, (4) each cell has exactly BYTES_PER_CELL bytes, (5) each proof has exactly BYTES_PER_PROOF bytes.",
