        "text": "construct_vanishing_polynomial (SG-022) MUST produce a polynomial that evaluates to 0 at all missing cell evaluation points and is nonzero at all present cell evaluation points. The coefficient spacing by FIELD_ELEMENTS_PER_CELL MUST correctly extend the polynomial to the full extended domain.",
